235
00:14:53,851 --> 00:14:55,436
Dois, deixe o futuro no passado.

236
00:14:55,520 --> 00:14:57,397
Melhorou. Vire aqui.

237
00:14:57,480 --> 00:14:58,648
Protocolo 3,

238
00:14:58,731 --> 00:15:01,734
